This script extracts annotation from Epigenome Roadmap and makes a plot for requested region.

Arguments:

chr: chr1/chr2/...
start position: start pos in hg19 
end position: start pos in hg19
graphic device: png/pdf
input Epigenome Roadmap file (optional): tab-delimited file to Roadmap Epigenomics data. If not specified, script downloads the data from AnnotationHub.

Usage: 

Rscript script_EpigenomeRoadmap.R chr3 57500000 58100000 png
